1. Ti *se slažeš* s mojim mišljenjem. (You *agree* with my opinion.)
2. Ja se ne *slažem* s tobom oko toga. (I don't *agree* with you about that.)
3. *Slažeš li* se s tim da je ovo najbolji način? (Do you *agree* that this is the best way?)
4. Oni *se ne slažu* s tim što si rekao. (They don't *agree* with what you said.)
5. Da li se *slažeš* da smo trebali drugačije postupiti? (Do you *agree* that we should have acted differently?)
6. Ona *se slaže* s njim u svemu. (She *agrees* with him in everything.)
7. Mi se *ne slažemo* s tim odlukama. (We *don't agree* with those decisions.)
8. *Slaže* se da je ovo teška situacija. (It *is agreed* that this is a difficult situation.)
9. Hoćeš li se *složiti* s našim planovima? (Will you *agree* with our plans?)
10. Njih dvoje se *ne slažu* oko toga gdje bi trebali otići na odmor. (The two of them *disagree* about where they should go on vacation.)